11 (1) is insolvent or in imminent danger of insolvency;
12 (2) is in an unsafe or unsound condition;
13 (3) has refused to pay its deposits or obligations in accordance
14 with the terms under which those deposits or obligations were
15 incurred;
16 (4) has refused to submit its records and affairs for inspection or
17 examination by the department or federal authorities;
18 (5) has violated any court order, statute, rule, or regulation of the
