5 identifying marks, numbers, names, letters, or special features.
6 (4) The amount of the loan.
7 (5) The date of the transaction.
8 (6) The serial number of the loan.
9 (7) The sum of the interest as provided in section 28 of this
10 chapter and the charge as provided in section 28.5 of this chapter
11 stated as an annual percentage rate computed in accordance with
