35 professional training and experience, financial responsibility, character,
36 and fitness of:
37 (1) the applicant;
38 (2) each executive officer, director, or manager of the applicant,
39 or any other individual having a similar status or performing a
40 similar function for the applicant; and
41 (3) if known, each person directly or indirectly owning of record
42 or owning beneficially at least ten percent (10%) of the
ES 169—LS 6567/DI 92

60
1 outstanding shares of any class of equity security of the applicant;
2 are such as to warrant belief that the business will be operated honestly
