6 (1) the time of application;
7 (2) the time of renewal of a license; or
8 (3) any other time considered necessary by the director.
9 (d) Evidence of compliance with this section must include:
10 (1) criminal background checks, as described in section 504 of
11 this chapter, including a national criminal history background
12 check (as defined in IC 10-13-3-12) by the Federal Bureau of
