1 voluntarily registers with the department to sponsor the
2 individual under IC 37-1-1-6(8) to engage solely as a third
3 party processor or underwriter.
4 (2) Unless the person or entity is compensated by:
5 (A) a creditor;
6 (B) a loan broker;
7 (C) another mortgage loan originator; or
8 (D) any agent of a creditor, a loan broker, or another
9 mortgage loan originator described in clauses (A) through
