1 creditor, and subject to section 17 of this chapter, the
2 imposition of a civil penalty not to exceed fifteen thousand
3 dollars ($15,000) for each practice, violation, or act that:
4 (A) is described in section 12 of this chapter; and
5 (B) is found to exist by the department or the director.
6 (d) A final order shall be issued in writing not later than ninety
