37 (e) A proceeding for review under this section must be initiated
38 not later than thirty (30) days after a copy of the order of the
39 department is received. If a proceeding is not initiated within the
40 time set forth in this subsection, the department may obtain a
41 decree of a civil court with jurisdiction for enforcement of the
42 department's order upon a showing that:
ES 169—LS 6567/DI 92

