6 percent (10%) or more, except that:
7 (1) the portion of the percentage change in the Index in excess
8 of a multiple of ten percent (10%) shall be disregarded and
9 the dollar amounts shall change only in multiples of ten
10 percent (10%) of the amounts on March 5, 1971;
