35 Sec. 12. "Consumer credit sale" is a sale of goods, services, or
36 an interest in land in which:
37 (1) credit is granted by a person who regularly engages as a
38 seller in credit transactions of the same kind;
39 (2) the buyer is a person other than an organization;
40 (3) the goods, services, or interest in land are purchased
41 primarily for a personal, family, or household purpose;
42 (4) either the debt is payable in installments or a credit service
