23 prepayment, as originally scheduled or as deferred.
24 Sec. 13. (a) For purposes of this section, "consumer credit sale"
25 includes a sale that is a sale of an interest in land and that is a first
26 lien mortgage transaction if the sale is otherwise a consumer credit
27 sale.
