1 (IC 37-2-6-9) and the provisions on civil actions by the department
2 (IC 37-2-7-14).
3 Sec. 15. (a) For the purposes of this section, "terms of the
4 refinancing" means:
5 (1) in the case of a fixed-rate consumer credit sale, the
6 individual payment amounts, the charges as a result of default
7 by the buyer, and the rate of the credit service charge; and
8 (2) in the case of a variable rate consumer credit sale, the
9 method used to determine the individual payment amounts,
10 the charges as a result of default by the buyer, the method
