34 minimum payment due that is not paid in full not later
35 than ten (10) days after its scheduled due date, in the case
36 of a consumer loan, refinancing, or consolidation that is
37 payable in a single installment that is due at least thirty
38 (30) days after the consumer loan, refinancing, or
39 consolidation is made. The amount of twenty-five dollars
40 ($25) in this clause is not subject to change under
41 IC 37-2-1-5.
