36 only to a loan agreement entered into before July 1, 2020. Except
37 as provided in subsection (b), upon prepayment in full of the
38 unpaid balance of a precomputed consumer loan, refinancing, or
39 consolidation, an amount not less than the unearned portion of the
40 loan finance charge calculated according to this section shall be
41 rebated to the debtor. If the rebate otherwise required is less than
42 one dollar ($1), no rebate need be made.
