9 If the deferral charge earned is less than the deferral charge paid,
10 the difference shall be added to the unearned portion of the loan
11 finance charge. If any part of a deferral charge has been earned
12 but has not been paid, that part shall be subtracted from the
13 unearned portion of the loan finance charge or shall be added to
14 the unpaid balance.
