13 pursuant to a consumer loan and that payment is to be made to the
14 assignee. A notification which does not reasonably identify the
15 rights assigned is ineffective. If requested by the debtor, the
16 assignee must seasonably furnish reasonable proof that the
17 assignment has been made and unless the assignee does so the
18 debtor may pay the original lender.
