37 to which the debtor would have been entitled had there been
38 no deferral, refinancing, or consolidation;
39 (3) the debtor receives a refund or credit on account of any
40 unexpired term of existing insurance in the amount that
41 would be required if the insurance were terminated under
42 section 6 of this chapter; and
