12 empowered to take the action. If the department is informed of a
13 violation or suspected violation by an insurer of this chapter, or of
14 the insurance laws, rules, and regulations of Indiana, the
15 department shall advise the insurance commissioner of the
16 circumstances.
17 Sec. 10. (a) To the extent that the commissioner's responsibility
18 under this chapter requires, the commissioner of insurance shall
19 issue rules with respect to insurers, and with respect to refunds
