37 information reasonably available. The records pertaining to any
38 transaction subject to this article shall be retained for two (2) years
39 after making the final entry relating to the consumer credit
40 transaction, but in the case of a revolving loan account or revolving
41 charge account, the two (2) years is measured from the date of each
42 entry.
