258
1 (A) the facts constituting the alleged violation, practice, or
2 breach;
3 (B) the facts alleged in support of the violation, practice, or
4 breach; and
5 (C) the director's intention to issue an order under section
6 20(a) of this chapter;
7 (3) be delivered to the board of directors of the creditor;
