27 the state comptroller two dollars and fifty cents ($2.50) of the
28 mortgage recording fee collected under IC 36-2-7-10(c)(2) for each
29 mortgage recorded by the county recorder. The state comptroller
30 shall deposit the money in the state general fund to be distributed
31 as described in section 3 of this chapter.
