33 state comptroller shall distribute one dollar and twenty-five cents
34 ($1.25) of the mortgage recording fee to the state general fund and
35 one dollar and twenty-five cents ($1.25) of the mortgage recording
36 fee to the homeowner protection unit account established by
37 IC 4-6-12-9.
